      <TextArea text="What is QuizTime?&#10;QuizTime is a modern JavaFX quiz app that brings trivia to life with a clean, responsive UI and questions fetched from the Open Trivia Database. Create an account, customize your quizzes, and track your progress over time.&#10;&#10;Key Features&#10;•  Personalized accounts: Register, log in, and manage your profile&#10;•  Flexible quizzes: Choose categories, difficulty (Easy/Medium/Hard), and types (Multiple Choice or True/False)&#10;•  Custom settings: Pick how many questions you want per quiz&#10;•  Real-time feedback: See correct/incorrect answers instantly&#10;•  Timer support: Add a challenge with timed sessions&#10;•  Progress tracking: View your history and best scores&#10;•  Smooth experience: Modern UI, theming, and animations&#10;•  Works offline for user data: Preferences and scores stored locally via SQLite&#10;&#10;How It Works&#10;1) Sign up or log in&#10;2) Configure your quiz (category, difficulty, type, number of questions)&#10;3) Take the quiz with instant scoring and a timer&#10;4) Review results and monitor improvement over time&#10;&#10;Powered By&#10;•  Java 21, JavaFX 24, Maven&#10;•  Open Trivia Database API for up-to-date questions&#10;•  SQLite for secure local storage&#10;&#10;Why You’ll Love It&#10;QuizTime balances simplicity and depth: quick to start, customizable when you want more control, and designed to help you learn, practice, and have fun.&#10;&#10;Privacy&#10;Your quiz preferences and scores are stored locally on your device in a lightweight SQLite database.&#10;&#10;Support&#10;Found an issue or have a feature idea? Visit our repository’s Issues and Discussions pages.&#10;•  Issues: https://github.com/yourusername/QuizTime/issues&#10;•  Discussions: https://github.com/yourusername/QuizTime/discussions&#10;&#10;Credits&#10;Made with love by Helal Anwar, with thanks to the Open Trivia Database, AtlantaFX, Ikonli, and the JavaFX community.&#10;&#10;Short version (if you need a compact variant)&#10;QuizTime is a modern JavaFX quiz app powered by the Open Trivia Database. Create an account, customize quizzes by category, difficulty, and type, get real-time feedback, and track your best scores—backed by local SQLite storage. Fast, clean, and fun." wrapText="true" VBox.vgrow="ALWAYS">
